    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. RH index predictions demonstrate adequate fidelity across all 5 operating points (max deviation 7.1%). The assessment team concludes the CFD model is sufficiently credible for its intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision consequence is HIGH; however, model influence is MEDIUM due to physical testing confirmation, yielding MRL 2 as appropriate. Accepted for regulatory submission support.",
